{"tid":1843713,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［預防肺炎］唔該叫你嗰棟樓嘅人記得倒水去廁所去水口","createTime":"2020-01-26T10:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T17:43:44.000Z","uid":167295,"like":131,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"6433dd8973a0562a5ad204d3b311b60cc9d74724","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打開過，不過推唔郁。<br />\n<br />\n當年淘大社區爆發就係因為個U型隔氣乾涸甚至被拆除，搞到抽返啲病毒入間屋。<br />\n<br />\n雖然未證實，但唔排除今次武漢肺炎係Airborne (SARS證實係Airborne)，所以喺屋企嘅預防措施都要做好，可以嘅話通知埋隔離左右、姨媽姑姐，自製文宣貼喺你棟樓部Lift 最好。一介粗人唔識畫到好靚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybqUgMH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybqUgMH.jpg&h=2fb00934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 早晚倒1:49嘅稀釋漂白水入去廁所去水口<br />\n<br />\n*政府建議係每次500毫升<br />\n<br />\n*留意返稀釋漂白水用凍水、同唔好諗住稀釋完一大桶存放下次用，咁樣會破功<br />\n<br />\n*仲有唔稀釋好易乸爛條喉<br />\n<br />\n*廁所去水口係指屎坑隔離，喺地下個去水口<br />\n因為平時只會拖地，所以呢一個去水口好容易會被忽略致乾涸。<br />\n<br />\n補返當年淘大個傳播途徑(cr: <a href=\"http://sun.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsun.on.cc&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGekUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=0d3d2552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">sun.on.cc</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0t9NBNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0t9NBNw.jpg&h=a3114f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係麻煩啲，但非常時期，港人自救。<br />\n你唔肯呼籲市民帶口罩，咪自己人呼籲。<br />\n你唔肯呼籲市民做預防措施，咪自己人呼籲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd827bbbd29e1384c8fa221138834758bb387a45","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"仲有記得倒完要洗手"},{"pid":"511f4caf16f444c6dccfaa220b12c4a4eb605b28","tid":1843713,"uid":316559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:20:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8ad1bb05a74d712c43da8b861e49c21420e2ca7","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"當你個政府三番四次賣港，港人惟有自保啦。"},{"pid":"13a14e079778f1d4ca2d49bbaed392048780fbaa","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce6656526831afb2b96c066f91ef1a5969705a70","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fea3ba8a45773bd930ab4fe8c0d63e404a6ebbe","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:23:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc7395660a00ff3b521955b4e0ea22221266113e","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4887b2e9445da9077e58c0a498694cdb74257341","tid":1843713,"uid":180402,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"冇哂漂白水就咁倒水得唔得"},{"pid":"d25bb34f78955349d3a38a1da480bb2a1cb72971","tid":1843713,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"唔係好明個原理<br />\n其實就咁牛皮膠紙封咗佢得唔得"},{"pid":"2a61b66c75c98e7abfbad4576b4a822132959a1f","tid":1843713,"uid":272287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:24:36.000Z","msg":"屋企個廚房都有個地下排水口 洗咪洗倒埋水？<br />\n有冇巴絲可以解答下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd44594a5b3d8828766e0ee7a962c0ac1891e1c","tid":1843713,"uid":167295,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"4887b2e9445da9077e58c0a498694cdb74257341","tid":1843713,"uid":180402,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"冇哂漂白水就咁倒水得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"都得，重點係保持條管濕潤，先發揮到隔氣嘅作用。<br />\n漂白水嘅功能係消毒。"},{"pid":"a24ae260eb38ac131bdc004cad52ac30c77f941e","tid":1843713,"uid":31317,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:26:13.000Z","msg"